<h4>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</h4>

<p>Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;" >
  <%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), style: "background-color: #1a5a96; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;" %>
</div>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
